<typeStatus id="7C6C18827735FFF4FC23FDE20F6D480A" box="[1018,1116,603,629]" pageId="14" pageNumber="395">holotype</typeStatus>
deposited in the Hungarian Natural History Museum (Budapest).
</paragraph>
